{"tid":1434681,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"應對AA 管制，應該敵進我退，敵退我進","createTime":"2019-08-09T00:21:13.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-09T02:26:50.000Z","uid":67812,"like":21,"dislike":7,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"4c8e76ff3fceea1bf2d74a01cf5ace1afd2732b8","tid":1434681,"uid":67812,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-09T00:21:13.000Z","msg":"隔離post 話唔去離境大堂，令AA 個管制變成最大既不合作活動<br />\n<br />\n朋友係機管局員工，嚟緊3日和你飛集會，想講幾句<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1434007\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1434007</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n唔好屌我係三毛左膠民意撚先，大家幻想下以下夢境<br />\n<br />\n8月9日，AA 係離境大堂做好準備set 好哂check point，發現現場零黑衫無示威者去，只有一大堆拖哂gip 打蛇餅既旅客<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong>AA 變左最大既不合作運動支持者<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></strong></span></span><br />\n<br />\n咁做既好處係直接入哂政府數，膚淺睇表面既淺藍中立甚至部份淺黃（例如我有心無腦既屋企人）都會發現政府有幾on9<br />\n<br />\n8月10日，AA係群眾壓力下解除限制，無哂check point 。突然有大班便衣市民入去離境大堂霸位，再一齊除衫，露出底下既黑衫<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong>和理非行動，正式開始</strong></span></span><br />\n<br />\n唔係叫大家屈服，錫羽毛，乜乜柒柒，只係唔好比政府牽住鼻頭走。佢地set 好哂陣地，我地仲衝過去，唔係勇武，係戰略失敗。我地最大既優勢就係有隱形大佬，可以高效高速就最新情況改變策略，用速度屌打政府<br />\n<br />\n只要各位<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">等一日，唔洗多，就係一日</span></strong></span>，唔好去離境大堂，到時政府不攻自破<br />\n重點係咁樣做無成本，我以上既建議無效咪第二日再去<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>敵進我退，敵退我進，香港係我地主場，要拎實個主動權</strong></span></span>"},{"pid":"e9e3e07a1c53eb2f54ce3836007d42bf8a72312e","tid":1434681,"uid":67812,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-09T00:21:30.000Z","msg":"自推十下"},{"pid":"b0488f52d54d038233b654de29319a62b2381d0b","tid":1434681,"uid":67812,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-09T00:21:48.000Z","msg":"我無野講"},{"pid":"a4f63f4a8769013507d822a763dc9e7900e4d2de","tid":1434681,"uid":67812,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-09T00:21:58.000Z","msg":"我無野講"},{"pid":"90c7b8ad074a5cb880939080aebc02151ba99ec8","tid":1434681,"uid":67812,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-09T00:22:08.000Z","msg":"我無野講"},{"pid":"1e6f58741a351cd63a3ca242d6a8fa61ac668620","tid":1434681,"uid":67812,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-09T00:22:18.000Z","msg":"我無野講"},{"pid":"bd6dc988bf77037d1b9652143ed38864b023cdb9","tid":1434681,"uid":67812,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-09T00:22:28.000Z","msg":"我無野講"},{"pid":"f10ad741f838e7699d223860af17bdfc7f8fecb1","tid":1434681,"uid":67812,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-09T00:22:38.000Z","msg":"我無野講"},{"pid":"e0333ad5e201b649a71ed3f932f630df9c2c2f62","tid":1434681,"uid":6845,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-09T00:23:07.000Z","msg":"你既前設係聽日唔封"},{"pid":"691d30d42b489fe56b1d2cea712605c7a3c12467","tid":1434681,"uid":67812,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"e0333ad5e201b649a71ed3f932f630df9c2c2f62","tid":1434681,"uid":6845,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-09T00:23:07.000Z","msg":"你既前設係聽日唔封"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-09T00:23:42.000Z","msg":"係，錯左咪聽日再去"},{"pid":"a34b4c436ca18e6cfbe0947e6adab565059fd09d","tid":1434681,"uid":67812,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-09T00:25:51.000Z","msg":"我無野講"},{"pid":"23fd1cd003e1d6eeb32f5b751b4174e38d8cc732","tid":1434681,"uid":67812,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-09T00:26:18.000Z","msg":"我無野講"},{"pid":"2a004808d02fe7bcbeadd6d75ef3975e9b845126","tid":1434681,"uid":2419,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-09T00:28:58.000Z","msg":"agge